 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">These gel-based cells have lower internal resistance, making them ideal for high-power applications. Combined with PD 3.1, a semi-solid-state power bank can deliver up to 140W, enough for a MacBook Pro 16 at full speed.</p>
